  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 840aed474ac71b81fa454e507b52bf90, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueTrigger
  dialogue:
    name: John Grunt
    sentences:
    - Hi, welcome to the prototype!
    - Here you can see network AI and traditional AI
    - Like landspaces, me, and other strangers (some of them are agressive)
    - 'Here''s a little story if you''re interested:

      Once upon a time, a guy
      decided to ask a manager if he wanted to see a huge project where they will
      be used in the traditional yearly tournament. '
    - 'The manager allowed him to do the business, and after a few months the project
      was ready to use. Everyone was happy. '
